    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The letter of acceptance of w.\nD. Haywood, now in Jail in Idaho\nfor completely in the murder of the\nlate Ex-Governor Steunenberg, of\nthe nomination for governor of\nColorado by the socialists, will be\nmade public in few days. A Spo-\nkane man who has read the docu-\nment states that one of its chief\nfeatures is a scathing arraignment\nof the Colorado supreme court."
